br />\n佢地係到耐過你 你做錯既野佢地都做錯過 都係咁行左過黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過佢都講左公司人事係好閪 因為女人多<br />\n啱啱入職場 好驚處理人事關係 所有野都好似同自己格格不入咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講 <br />\n好多謝你啊同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係到掙扎緊既大家 都要努力！！"},{"pid":"e757ddebacda863011ddeb8bfba3b15262ae1f77","tid":2163412,"uid":346801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"一個月之後既自己 多謝今日既你選擇左留低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為咁你就有糧出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38722d02353b79cfb603b7c4d02833b63cf47bd3","tid":2163412,"uid":346801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e67976c7d5213d8c3a2bc4501478025ce0f32a9","tid":2163412,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"又要驚又要做<br />\n去到邊都比人蝦啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"係！ 我會強大啲！但要啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定點樣可以冇咁驚"},{"pid":"d64b0231108855986d962aff89f779a270270fda","tid":2163412,"uid":346801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"569b40125721494996cc19c013670e076f1b021a","tid":2163412,"uid":62260,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6c6b83841002a14dac20478fb7a205e20f219ed0","tid":2163412,"uid":346801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返左半個月 做啲好基本既野都可以好多甩漏<br />\n日日都俾同事問候<br />\n極大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗起起身返去又要俾成班同事望住。。<br />\n又好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗左幾次想辭。。但如果咁小野都克服唔到以後點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/